              <h4 class="tos-plain-language-heading">Basically...</h4>
              <div class="rich-text w-richtext">
                <p>Our blogs and community forums are accessible to the public, so any information provided in these areas, including your personal information, may be read, collected, and used by the public. If you need personal info removed, you can emails us at <a href="mailto:contact@webflow.com">contact@webflow.com</a> and we’ll remove it, if possible.</p>
